item.description:
Free Introductory Talk

What Is Wicca? What it is not.....

Questions & Answers

Discussion of new Witchcraft Training Series
Class Content for each Level

This discussion group is for beginners who want to learn about
what wicca is truly about, and also for those more advanced in the craft who would like to join the discussion and learn more about the class content of my upcoming Witchcraft Training Series.....

Complementary Appetizers

Come join us for of a night of discussion and fun! :)

Directions: 290 South, to 395 South, Take exit 2, Webster, the exit veers to the right, follow to the end at the light, take a left, onto Main St.
Go to the center of town, and Edward's Emporium is on the right, right next to The Party Planner.

If you have trouble with the directions, call me at: (508) 847-7677 and I will help! :)
item.why: We are going to have a great discussion about what wicca truly is ( a new age religion!) and I will be going through what will be covered in my 6 class series. There will also be time for questions and answers, and some goodies to eat, to boot! :)
item.name: Free Wicca Discussion: The Truth About Wicca
